headline: This 5.6%-Yielding Dividend Stock Keeps Finding New Ways to Grow
summary: Vici Properties (NYSE: VICI) owns one of the largest collections of gaming, hospitality, and entertainment destinations in the country.  Its real estate portfolio features many of the most iconic casinos on the Las Vegas Strip, including Caesars Palace Las Vegas and The Venetian Resort Las Vegas.  While it's already a leading owner of experiential real estate, Vici Properties continues to find new ways to expand.
